## Why This Is Asked
Tests practical DR planning for serverless stacks, emphasizing automation, data replication choices, and safe testing.

## Key Concepts
- AWS Global Accelerator and multi-region endpoints
- Route 53 health checks and failover routing
- Lambda versioning and canary deployments
- DynamoDB Global Tables and S3 cross-region replication
- Canary DR testing and rollback workflows

